These were newer production when I got them, and have been properly stored for the last 2 years, so they'll last you a LONG time.  Contents are all Government-contract (actual MREs).  There are 16 entree/side-dishes, something like 30 peanut butter, chocolate-peanut butter, and cheese packets, a few packets of crackers and other snacks, 2-3 dozen water-activated food heaters, assorted condiments/accessory items, plastic beverage bags, probably 20 packs of waterproof matches, and more. title: For Sale:   SIG P220-Browning Double Action .45 ACP
postcontent:
SIG P220-Browning Double Action .45 ACP- Yes the subject is correct. 
In 1976 Schweizerische Industrie Gesellschaft (SIG) introduced what would become the P220, manufactured by Sauer.  Sig Sauer contracted with Browning Arms Co.  to import the gun as the Browning Double Action (BDA). The P220 was initially imported to the US by Browning from 1977-1980 prior to Sig establishing a presence in the US. In 1980 Sig decided to import them into the US on their own. This P220 is a must have for the Sig or Browning collector.  It's in great shape and has the 3 correct Browning and Sig Sauer markings (Browning Arms Co., Morgan Utah & Montreal on the left side of the slide, and Sig Sauer System, Made in W. Germany on the right side) and correct Browning logo hard plastic grips. Please note that the pistol is posted on another gun board and is subject to prior sale. Originally posted at $675.00 is has been reduced to $575.00 as I need additional funds for an optic. More pics available-

Manufacturer's supply of AR platform weapons are slowly coming back.  Magazine supply is coming back.  Ammo prices have peaked and supply will come back also.

Be diligent in protecting our right to keep and bear arms but be disciplined.  Don't play into the self fulfilling cycle of rewarding scalpers who snatch up the ammo we want and then sell it back to us!!!!!

When these scalpers start to get stuck sitting on their inventories of overpriced guns, magazines, and ammo we will really see prices drop and product become available to those of us who enjoy the sport for the right reasons!
